snippet: Dismayed at dropping the first set after being a single point from taking it, Serena Williams sat in her Centre Court sideline chair and cracked her racket against the turf once, twice, three times, four....
lead_paragraph: Dismayed at dropping the first set after being a single point from taking it, Serena Williams sat in her Centre Court sideline chair and cracked her racket against the turf once, twice, three times, four.

headline.print_headline: Serena Survives at Wimbledon, Racket Doesn't; Djokovic Down
